data.description: Check out this cute rambler in the heart of Rose Park! Three beds and one bath, with an updated kitchen that includes island range and granite countertops. Front room features fire place and two large windows to let in plenty of light. Unfinished basement has been framed and insulated, so you can easily make it your own. Just minutes from downtown SLC, with convenient freeway access. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from Salt Lake County tax data. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
